Copa de Oro (Los Angeles) 1987

Friendly Tournament
Los Angeles Memorial Colisseum, Los Angeles, California

Participant Teams:
Dundee United (Scotland)
AS Roma (Italy)
Vasco da Gama (Brazil)
Rosario Central (Argentina)
Guadalajara (Mexico)
América (Mexico)

Group Phase

Round 1
[Jun 11]
